  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This tattoo is a series of six concentric circles that show up as a soft yellow on any skin tone. The marks carry in them a protective force that bolsters your body and soul. The first time each day that someone attempts to Treat your Wounds and rolls a critical failure, they get a failure instead.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> command</p><p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> For 5 rounds, your entire body begins to glow, with the effects of a 1st-rank @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.WBmvzNDfpwka3qT4]{Light} spell. At the end of each of your turns during this time, you regain @Damage[1d4[healing]]{1d4 Hit Points}.</p>"
